I have been enjoying the Ravi Shankar, Ustaad Bismillah ,Lata ,Rafi ,Mukesh ,Kishore ,Jagjit Chitra and many many Indian singers along with Nur Jahan, Mehdi Hassan,Rushdi ,Shahnaz Begum, Mehnaz ,Nayyera Noor, and many many more all my life.
We just have to enjoy music, not to indulge in politics on these pages, there are other forms ,where we can discuss our political views and sentiments.

The fine arts are to nourish  the most civilized ,cultured ,sensetive and heart touching ways of expression. It is totally unacceptable to use
Abusive language ,Galam Galuch.
After hearing a beautiful Sofiana Kalaam from Rahat , Ghazal from Ali Sethi, A Kaafi,A Heer , one has to become a better human and not digging oneself to the Lowest of Low
